            "Apply defibrillation pads early",
            "Escalate per CPP006 as early as practicable",
            "CPR rate: 100\u2013120/min | Depth: \u22655cm | Full recoil",
            "No SGA: 30:2 ratio, pause for ventilations",
            "SGA/ETT: 15:1 ratio, 6\u20138 breaths/min, no pause",
            "Defibrillate at 2-minute intervals: Apex L mid-axillary 6th ICS, Sternal R upper chest"
