            "Excessive shortness of breath on exertion or at rest",
            "Diaphoresis (excessive sweating)",
            "Blood-tinged or pink sputum (severe)",
            "Significant hypertension (especially with left ventricular dysfunction)",
            "Dependent oedema",
            "Crackles on chest auscultation",
            "Orthopnoea (worse breathing lying flat)"
          ],
          "memory_items": [
