              "text": "IV access \u2014 RN (TE) and RNCC only",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 11,
              "text": "Adrenaline 1mg IV: repeat every 4 minutes (every 2nd cycle) \u2014 RNCC only",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 12,
              "text": "Amiodarone 300mg IV if VF/VT after 3rd shock \u2014 RNCC only",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 13,
              "text": "Amiodarone 150mg IV if VF/VT persists after 5th shock \u2014 RNCC only",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 14,
              "text": "Flush all medications with 20\u201330ml normal saline \u2014 RNCC only",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 15,
              "text": "ROSC (signs of life present): Optimise airway, ventilate 12\u201316/min via BVM (100% O2), 12-lead ECG where accredited",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "step": 16,
              "text": "No signs of life: Refer to Appendix 2 Withholding/ceasing resuscitation",
              "note": ""
            }
          ],
          "special_notes": [
            {
              "text": "Hypothermic cardiac arrest (<30\u00b0C): Double the interval for adrenaline and amiodarone",
              "scopes": [
